IAeDefVisitor
public class AeProcessViewPropertyBuilder
extends AeProcessWebPropertyBuilder

This class is responsible for building the list of properties to be displayed by the AePropertViewBean. Any state information that is to be displayed, such as variables, is retrieved by this class.
